@startuml
start

:Receive interaction from supported channel;
:Normalize payload into Case intake request;
:Validate required fields and file constraints;

if (Validation passed?) then (Yes)
  :Create or update Contact candidate;
  :Verify citizen by phone/email with MDM;
  if (Verification successful?) then (Yes)
    :Link verified Contact and MDM reference;
  else (No)
    :Set Manual Review verification status;
    :Log integration or verification exception when applicable;
  endif
  :Create Case with Enquiry or Feedback record type;
  :Attach uploaded files using Salesforce Files;
  :Apply SLA policy and routing attributes;
  :Route through Omni-Channel or queue;
  :Notify citizen and assigned team;
else (No)
  :Return validation message to channel;
endif

stop
@enduml
